 />\n黑驚真心為香港！<br />\n唔好擺人地仔女天真對話相片上網！<br />\n<br />\n4) 落club見到黑驚<br />\n可以同佢玩ONS <br />\n咁事後萬一畀佢疑似老強非禮都唔好告佢！<br />\n忍一忍好了 唔好攪大佢！"},{"pid":"58656907c7c32321df6265703420fd6705d9f099","tid":1210622,"uid":51090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f14ee318675329276bf1070f6227d014a25d39c8","tid":1210622,"uid":34263,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:34:20.000Z","msg":"一定唔會噴得曬, 噴曬支那都仲會有"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:42:03.000Z","msg":"支那邊會嘥咁多錢買裝備俾公安<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地用開拳頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f99511df02855a4e33662c1d96fded0496f64fb","tid":1210622,"uid":216432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:43:03.000Z","msg":"係都去北角攞啦 點會去機場攞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"396af835ea151befa36540dc674d06d9a671b1e6","tid":1210622,"uid":51090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c97e4632c273cd0fc0c536a89a56a3ccafd09cdf","tid":1210622,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:40:46.000Z","msg":"消耗佢地儲備<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:43:33.000Z","msg":"隨時要限制警犬1支要用成日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e48de69af3575afd1a497eef389920fff9ba4fc7","tid":1210622,"uid":101048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:43:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84a2d4748196cc81e24a36b072eadaacc78e013f","tid":1210622,"uid":51090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3f99511df02855a4e33662c1d96fded0496f64fb","tid":1210622,"uid":216432,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T14:43:03.000Z","msg":"係都去北角攞啦 點會去機場攞 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"repl